Description: 10 fragments of Coptic codex pages. Twelve frames (EA 76565-76) are stored together in an archival box.
Curator's comments: EA 76415 may belong to the same group.

Previously unregistered material stored in Papyrus Store. The frame labelled in various hands 'Sept. - 1847-1848. No 276- No 310(?)1 H No 5'. Twelve frames (EA 76565-76) are stored together in an archival box.
Acquisition notes: 'Gift of papyri from Hartwell House by Messrs Rutter and Marchant.'
